HEADWORD: Cymry
<hw>Cym"ry</hw> <pr>(-r?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[W.,
<ets>pl</ets>.]</ety> <def>A collective term for the Welsh race; -- so
called by themselves .</def> <altsp>[<asp>Written also Cymri</asp>,
<asp>Cwmry</asp>, <asp>Kymry</asp>, etc.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
